About Us
21st Annual Florida State Bluegrass & Chili Cook-off  Festival – Forest Capital State Park in Perry. Tickets are on sale now!
This very popular event attracts thousands each year for bluegrass music, music workshops, arts and crafts, food vendors, chili cook-off and FREE Moon Pies! This event was chosen by the international Bluegrass Music Association as one of the best events in the entire country in 2006.
For more information about vending or tickets got to
www.floridastatebluegrass.com
or call 850-584-5366.  This event is held the first weekend in April each year.
